The Personal **Animation Notifies** window displays custom Animation Notifies created in the Asset Editor.

The **Animation Notifies** window is not visible by default. To view it, on Persona's **Window** menu, click **Animation Notifies**.

![Animation Notifies Window](AnimationNotifies.png)

[REGION:note]
Selecting a custom Animation Notify in the **Animation Notifies** window exposes its properties in Persona's **Details** panel.
[/REGION]

To delete a custom Animation Notify, **Right-click** it, and then click **Delete**.

To rename a custom Animation Notify, **Right-click** it, and then click **Rename**.

For more information about Persona's **Asset Editor**, see [](Engine/Animation/Persona\AssetEditor).
